		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just to quantify this: I measured the video lag on my Magnavox SDTV and my Vizio HDTV using a 60 fps camcorder and <a href="http://pics.pineight.com/nes/bunny250.zip" class="postlink">a ROM that I banged out in a few minutes</a> that turns the backdrop color white while A is held.<br /><br /><img src="http://pineight.com/mw/images/0/05/HDTV_vs_SDTV_lag.gif" alt="Image" /><br />Button-to-video lag at 1/30 speed<br /><br />SDTV: nice and immediate<br />HDTV: four fields (~67 ms) lag

		

